Comment: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:32.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,その腕に絡んだ時計の針は
Comment: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:33.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:38.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,狂わないなんて信じていないで
Comment: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:45.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,進もうと急かすような秒針
Comment: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:51.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,巻き戻そう 抓んだ竜頭回し
Comment: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:55.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇想夢譚になっていく
Comment: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:58.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,曖昧が依然あるなら
Comment: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,触れて確かめてしまえばいいよ
Comment: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,現実を脱がせて
Comment: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:07.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let me hightail it out of here
Comment: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:10.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,繰り返すほど牴牾しい
Comment: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,儚いって知りながら 求めてしまう
Comment: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,背徳の夢
Comment: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:32.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,缠绕在你腕上的时针
Comment: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:38.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,毋庸置疑会行至疯狂
Comment: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:45.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,仿佛在催促前行的秒针
Comment: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:51.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,拧动发条 让我们逆转时光吧
Comment: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:55.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,坠入梦幻奇谭
Comment: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:58.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,若暧昧仍旧存在
Comment: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,亲自触碰来确认这一切
Comment: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,褪去现实的桎梏
Comment: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:10.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,越是重演便越显矛盾
Comment: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,明知虚幻 却仍执于追寻
Comment: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,这场背德之梦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------STAFF----------
